We are here to help you!

We share our customer’s concerns and are working hard to keep all our vehicles and services available to all those in need.
To protect renters and team members, we recently escalated our already high standard of readying vehicles.  We added specific steps, including:
•	Sanitize EVERY Steering wheel
•	Sanitize EVERY Interior  and Exterior  Door Handle
•	Sanitize EVERY Radio and Temperature Control Knob
•	Sanitize EVERY Key and Key-Tag / Fob
•	Sanitize EVERY Seat/Seatbelt
If you have any questions or concerns, please don’t hesitate to ask, or make us aware.
                                                          Thank you!

Hello and thank you for your interest in my vehicles!  🚘 My name is Darwin and I am very passionate about making sure you have a great experience with me. I am excited to help you have a safe, productive and fun trip whether it is for business 💼 or leisure 🏄‍♀️.  We are located very close to downtown Dallas and not far from DFW or Lovefield airport ✈️. 

Thank you for your support and kind reviews ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ which we hope are helpful to our new customers!  We look forward to seeing you when you come to the Dallas-Ft. Worth area!

Quick Notes about our service:

- Please download the Turo app on your phone, all our communications are through the chat feature on the app

- Tolls are not included (it also applies to DFW Airport tolls).  We will bill you via the Turo app 5-7 business days after the end of your trip.

- Be prepared to send us a selfie of you holding your driver's license next to your face, this is a Turo requirement for remote deliveries.

And don't forget to check out our vehicle line-up!

Mid Size Sedans:
⏩2014 Honda Civic
⏩2015 Kia Forte

⏩2015 Mercedes Benz E400 (Luxury Edition)

Safe travels!

- Darwin

Hello, my name is Erika and I'm an all-star Turo host looking to provide guests with a safe and reliable vehicle for their next adventure. Whether you need to book a vehicle for business or leisure I am looking to accommodate you and provide you with the best customer service along the way!

Welcome to GL Enterprises! ✨We’re excited you’re here and would love to share our cars with you! 

Life has brought us many different passions but two things remain the same - we truly enjoy taking care of people and life is just too short not to travel. 

As guests ourselves, we’ve been on both sides of these experiences and aim to provide nothing less than 5 🌟 VIP service.  If there’s anything we can do to accommodate you, please just let us know and we will do everything possible!

We currently have 8 cars in our fleet with plans to expand and diversify in the next year. Whether you’re looking for a luxurious, one of a kind experience or something dependable to get your family where they need to go, we’ll have something for you at an affordable price! 

We can’t wait to host you!
